INSERT INTO public.events VALUES (271078315274279, 'Cebu Hacktoberfest 2023', 'Join us in celebrating open source with a bang!

Hacktoberfest is a month-long celebration of Open Source Software hosted by DigitalOcean. Hacktoberfest brings together open-source enthusiasts, beginners, and the global developer community and encourages them to contribute to open-source projects.

For Cebu, it will be a one-day, whole day event on Saturday, October 28, 2023, at From Here Co-Working Space, Crossroads Mall!

We will talk about what is Open Source Software and how to contribute to it, highlight open-source projects by Cebuanos, and hold breakout coding sessions for people to contribute to the presented projects.

This event will be spearheaded by Javascript Cebu, with the support of the Cebu Tech Communities. Also, a quick mention to share with you all the 10th anniversary of PizzaPy! 😊

Happy hacking! #Hacktoberfest

---

⚙️⚒️ Maintainers:

Got an open source project you want to share? Follow this link and add your repo: https://dub.sh/cebhck2023repo

---

Students, professionals, and all, join us in this whole day event by registering here: https://dub.sh/cebuhacktoberfest23

---

Huge thanks to our Event Partner - From Here and Corporate Sponsor - LegalMatch Philippines and Open source Sponsor - StacksJS

---

Schedule:

