INSERT INTO public.events VALUES (417057349096291, 'Laravel Codecamp Exclusive for USC Students', 'What is Laravel?

Laravel is an open-source PHP framework. Laravel reuses the existing components of different frameworks which helps in creating a web application. The web application thus designed is more structured and pragmatic.
Laravel offers a rich set of functionalities which incorporates the basic features of PHP frameworks like CodeIgniter, Yii and other programming languages like Ruby on Rails. Laravel has a very rich set of features which will boost the speed of web development.

Advantages of Laravel
Laravel offers you the following advantages, when you are designing a web application based on it −
1. The web application becomes more scalable, owing to the Laravel framework.
2. Considerable time is saved in designing the web application, since Laravel reuses the components from other framework in developing web application.
3. It includes namespaces and interfaces, thus helps to organize and manage resources.

DevCon Cebu together Laravel Cebu will hold an exclusive codecamp for USC students with the course outline below:
- Introduction to Laravel
- Build mini-facebook with Laravel  called "Larabook".
- Basic user authentication
- Creating timeline basic view
-  Post status to timeline
- Display posts to timeline
- Build search displaying posts & users
- Coding  and Q&A

Would you like to have this at your school or your office?
Contact us now.', '2019-06-22 00:00:00+00', '2019-06-22 09:00:00+00', '2024-10-17 01:36:16.505+00', 'USC Talamban Campus', 417057349096291, NULL, NULL, 'https://scontent.fceb1-5.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.6435-9/59740032_1050099915184593_7478588027221049344_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=478c00&_nc_eui2=AeE5POvKA6CSwWsCq7PtSnmYWsh-Ut5PH-FayH5S3k8f4SVhXVcmf1uWy13LDDsbvZc&_nc_ohc=zlRr2y6b9GMQ7kNvgGRL9bJ&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.fceb1-5.fna&edm=ABTKTjYEAAAA&_nc_gid=AIEv-87PSYRC8b2Mw-18mVR&oh=00_AYBpB18JYBWUcdaQYiD5KAXY0XlOg_R4pzEeKJnmxwuUaQ&oe=6737D339', false, NULL, false, NULL, 'laravel-codecamp-exclusive-for-usc-students-417057349096291');
